<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA524_07_IH_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema524_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_07_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star2" lang="y">어떤 수에 0.5를 곱해야 하는데 잘못하여 더했더니 0.77이 되었습니다. 옳게 계산한 값을 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center">
            <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">어떤 수를 구해 보세요.</p>
            <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
              (
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="0.27"></math-field>
              </div>
              )
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center">
            <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">옳게 계산한 값을 구해 보세요.</p>
            <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
              (
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="0.135"></math-field>
              </div>
              )
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">
                  어떤 수를 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>라고 하면 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span> +0.5=0.77이므로 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>=0.77-0.5=0.27입니다.
                  <br />
                  따라서 어떤 수는 0.27입니다.
                </p>
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">0.27×0.5=0.135이므로 옳게 계산한 값은 0.135입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
